skrang
share many characteristics. Scavian characters should begin play with Rank =
1 in
each of the Sailing, Swimming, and Melee Weapons skills.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>They usually d=
o not
follow the way of the Cavalryman. They sometimes become Sky Raiders by earn=
ing
the respect of troll Sky Raiders through exceptional displays of leadership
during battle. At the gamemaster‚Äôs discretion, Scavian characters may pur=
sue the
Boatman Discipline, even though this is normally restricted to t‚Äôskrang o=
nly.</p>

