her
races, k‚Äôstulaami get along well with all but the t‚Äôskrang of the Serpe=
nt. Many
k‚Äôstulaami resent the Serpent River t‚Äôskrang for treating them as mutan=
ts
rather than kin.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>K‚Äôstulaami u=
se many
types of weapons, often developing unique ways of fighting using weapons ta=
ken
from adventurers who bother or harass the k‚Äôstulaami community. They use =
only
the lightest types of armor, so that they can glide unimpeded.</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>K‚Äôstulaami g=
ain the
Gliding ability as an additional Racial Ability:</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>Gliding: The
character can glide through the air after leaping from a position higher th=
an
his body height. He can perform his movement for the round in a glide rather
