<p style=3D'margin:0in;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt'>A t‚Äôskrang b=
egins
life with two Names, one chosen by its egg parent before the hatchling brea=
ks
its shell, and the second the Name of the foundation into which it is born.=
 At
kaissa, when the hatchling becomes an adult, it chooses its third Name, som=
etimes
